<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>My ginger is just as laid back yet super energetic, I’ve had neighbours come up to me telling me about how he chases the dogs like a game of tag haha. </p>
<p>He’s such a people’s person that I often forget he’s a cat and not a human, even though he acts like it. And he surely lives up to his name, I’m constantly asking my hubby “where’s Wally ?” Only to find him hiding in some cupboard or one of his boxes</p>
<p>I love ginger kitty’s even more now thanks to this nugget</p>
