<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-38550' data-commentid="38550" data-postid="3334" data-belowelement="comment-38550" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Ed" aria-label='Reply to Ed'>Reply</a> <span>&darr;</span> </div>
