<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>i have ginger cat but hes a bit shy 12 weeks old</p>
</section>
<div class="reply">
<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-39221' data-commentid="39221" data-postid="3334" data-belowelement="comment-39221" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to cat" aria-label='Reply to cat'>Reply</a> <span>&darr;</span> </div>
