<p>Our ginger and white cat (Tiger) is huge at 6 months at 34cm height and weighing 5.5kg&#8230; highly intelligent and has no fear, very friendly and when we talk to him, he replies back his language&#8230; he wakes us up to go out at night. Is his size normal&#8230; looks like a tiger pup.</p>
