<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>Last month a ginger cat came home it was lost. So i gave food everyday. Now the cat is fixed in our home. Likes to sleep on chair. If it see one dog in compound, cat will chase tge dog. We can play few min with it. But then it will start to bite or scratch. It doesn&#8217;t do anything to female cat coming in our compound. But will not leave male cat. It likes to sleep on my legs. Wen i sit on chair. We dont leave cats to come in house. But ginger cat come in by meow. Other cat come in hiding. Our cat protects us from dogs, snakes. BUT it doesn&#8217;t like other people coming our home.</p>
</section>
