<p>I have 2 Ginger boys. Milo will be 12 y/o and Taz the Spaz will be 9 y/o. Taz weighs 22 lbs and will only eat dry cat food and refuses to even look at wet food. They are constantly together and will not sleep unless they are touching each other. Taz fetches tennis balls like a dog and Milo is EXTREMELY needy and wakes me up for attention at all hours of the night. I wouldn’t trade them for anything. They have my heart and soul!! </p>
</section>
