<p>I have a ginger cat named Garfield he&#8217;s definitely a mummy&#8217;s boy lol he&#8217;s very playful but a snuggle pot too. But I could really use some advice.. hubby and I believe he has been mistreated by our old housemates daughters because he has become very skittish and hides every time he hears or sees kids. But another problem we have with him is he&#8217;s toilet trained but he&#8217;s literally going everywhere including on our bed! PLEASE help we&#8217;ve tried everything and nothing is working it&#8217;s been happening since the end of 2020 and we&#8217;ve had him since he was 7 weeks old</p>
