<p>I had a ginger cat named Jake who lived to be 18. He was the best. I called him my puppy cat. He&#8217;d sleep behind my head with his chin on my forehead. I l9 ed him so much. 12 years later I adopted a 6 yr old ginger &amp; white boy &amp; called him Zevon. He loves all people &amp; hates all animals. He is a big floofy beautiful guy who loves to go outside in his harness. He loves prey play. He has diabetes which was discovered 2 months ago. I am happy I have him so I can be sure he gets the treatment he deserves.</p>
